videos.headline: Russell comes up clutch with 41 points in OT win for URI
videos.description: Rhode Island's Fatts Russell hits a few clutch 3-pointers down the stretch, including one with five seconds left in regulation on the way to an overtime win vs. Saint Joseph's.
